Generic stream writer Output file in OV format with EEG signal and markers

External Stimulator This SSVEP scenario needs to run along with an external application. The application is run automatically after the start of the scenario. The stimulator accepts two keyboard commands: Pressing <Space> will send a start stimulation to the scenario and the experiment will begin. Pressing <Escape> will quit the stimulator and stop the scenario.

SSVEP Training Controller SSVEP scenario for the training phase, a marker points at the target the user has to look at. A prescribe sequence of stimuli is shown to the user. Stimulation duration, break duration and flickering delay can be changed. For Target Position and Target Size check "trainer" file and please make sure that it has the following path: C:\Users\User\Desktop\openvibe\share\openvibe\applications\ssvep-demo
